{"tid":2042562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底高可晴老豆係邊個，居然到而家都無人起到佢出嚟。","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T02:31:18.000Z","uid":186882,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8cc807b8b6214c426bf00db812293626f5e80d","tid":2042562,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"這女子後台睇黎硬到唔起佢底唔得，連大波樺都要睇佢頭<br />\n傳媒到而家都未起到佢底<br />\n老豆搵仔又無佢老豆資料<br />\n權力會唔會連燉餅強都要睇佢頭？<br />\n講真之前黑警藏冰案燉都保唔到佢（或者燉借毒老屈啦）<br />\n如果要穩軍心，黑警藏冰都唔應該爆出嚟啦<br />\n<br />\n但高可晴老豆神秘程度仲高過朱緩老豆<br />\n仲威過我爸是李剛<br />\n非常之可疑<br />\n如果起到佢老豆出嚟，好可能仲起到背後利益集團<br />\n<br />\n真係諗起都扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db92d641ab63dc47a8d2828638bb372b1cacc718","tid":2042562,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起左啦 唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7c34c3bfdca1ed550c2b24db80a0729e6bc742","tid":2042562,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db92d641ab63dc47a8d2828638bb372b1cacc718","tid":2042562,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起左啦 唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:46:40.000Z","msg":"起咗我完全search唔到，有可能咩？"},{"pid":"c0419ebecd7d6edc65f36786cfa3c4d97fd101f9","tid":2042562,"uid":63734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":